## Intention: ignore app secrets in .secret files anywhere (regardless, storing secrets in plain-text is bad practice)

*.secret
*.secrets



## Intention: ignore .log files anywhere

*.log
*.logs



## Intention: ignore loose I/O artifacts anywhere

*.input
*.inputs
*.output
*.outputs



## Intention: ignore non-example .env files anywhere

*.env
*.env.*
!.env.*example



## Intention: ESLINT: ignore eslint caches anywhere

*.eslintcache



## Intention: iOS: ignore iOS filesystem detritus anywhere

*.icloud



## Intention: TS: ignore TypeScript build artifacts anywhere in the project, including if they accidentally sneak into the root or a source directory

*.tsbuildinfo



## Intention: SVELTE: ignore sveltekit, svelte, and vite build artifacts anywhere in the project

*.DS_Store
*.vercel
*.output
vite.config.js.timestamp-*
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*
